{"tid":1627101,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民記民調要人！！","createTime":"2019-10-05T14:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T17:07:21.000Z","uid":272375,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9debe7bd4da36b2750efb13fd3d50b63588ab807","tid":1627101,"uid":272375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:27:14.000Z","msg":"民記tg啱啱出咗新民調比大家表達下對蒙面法嘅意見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><blockquote>【民間記者會之民調又來了】<br />\n<br />\n香港政府喺電光火石之間推行《禁止蒙面規例》，喺唔緊急嘅情況下實施咗《緊急情況規例條例》。大家對呢條例又點睇呢？<br />\n<br />\n快啲入黎表達你對禁蒙面法嘅意見啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.citizenspc.org/survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org%2Fsurvey&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=b6559bb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.citizenspc.org/survey</a><br />\n<br />\n問卷截止時間為10月6日(星期日)晚上9時59分。<br />\n<br />\n再一次多謝大家對民間記者會嘅支持！</blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n限期係聽晚十點前<br />\n大家見到幫手推下<br />\n<br />\nP牌仔推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://t.me/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=1fb2d108\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/citizenspresscon</a>"},{"pid":"75cbe913c277a271b2c911bb66df1d6ce341b09a","tid":1627101,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"填左，但會唔會長過頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce32d8e5da95b8f7803ecadc90c941a945fe936","tid":1627101,"uid":78186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:36:14.000Z","msg":"完成"},{"pid":"3a78bc9df0851d1d93096cd4fb8370a31ffb23bf","tid":1627101,"uid":173883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:43:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db0b54d51a9e4c57c6f027a04e19558b79ab3de0","tid":1627101,"uid":2836,"like":